#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:15
msgid "Transitions"
msgstr "Prehodi"

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:17
msgid ""
"Video transition is a post-production technique to connect shots (clips) and "
"tie them together into a cohesive and polished storyline. Depending on what "
"mood or tone you want to convey, suggest passage of time, or tell different "
"parts of the story or even show parallel story line, different transitions "
"can and should be used. It is part of the creative process of film making."
msgstr ""
"Video prehod je poprodukcijska tehnika za povezovanje posnetkov (kadrov) in "
"njihovo povezovanje v kohezivno in izdelano pripoved. Glede na to, kakšno "
"razpoloženje ali ton želite prenesti, predlagati potek časa ali povedati "
"različne dele zgodbe ali celo prikazati vzporedno zgodbo, se lahko in morajo "
"uporabiti različni prehodi. Je del ustvarjalnega procesa izdelovanja filmov."

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:19
msgid ""
"In Kdenlive, transitions are part of :doc:`compositions <compositions>`. "
"After all, you are compositing two clips albeit for a different purpose. But "
"the workflow is very similar. And because transitions are added as "
"compositions, the two terms are often used interchangeably. Just keep in "
"mind that they are used for different purposes in video editing."
msgstr ""
"V Kdenlive so prehodi del :doc:`sestav <compositions>`. Navsezadnje "
"sestavljate dva posnetka, čeprav za drug namen. Toda potek dela je zelo "
"podoben. In ker so prehodi dodani kot sestave, se oba izraza pogosto "
"uporabljata zamenljivo. Ne pozabite, da se uporabljata za različne namene "
"pri urejanju videa."

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:21
msgid "There are two ways to transition between clips:"
msgstr "Med posnetkoma lahko prehajate na dva načina:"

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:23
msgid ""
":doc:`Mixes</compositing/transitions/mixes>`, also called **same-track "
"transitions**, between two adjacent clips in the same track"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Miksi</compositing/transitions/mixes>`, imenovani tudi **prehodi na "
"isti stezi**, med dvema soležnima posnetkoma v isti stezi"

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:24
msgid ""
":doc:`transitions/composite_transitions` between overlapping clips on "
"different tracks"
msgstr ""
":doc:`prehodi<transitions/composite_transitions>` med prekrivajočimi se "
"posnetki na različnih stezah"

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:26
msgid ""
"Available transitions range from built-in presets to wipes with different "
"methods and the ability to use your own greyscale images in :file:`.pgm` "
"(Portable Grey Map) format. Most wipes (and the same applies to Dissolve and "
"Luma) are essentially greyscale images under the hood. During the "
"transition, the composition track\\ [1]_ will be displayed in the darkest "
"part of the wipe image first; if the wipe transition is inverted, the "
"composition track will become visible in the brightest area of the wipe "
"image first."
msgstr ""
"Razpoložljivi prehodi segajo od vgrajenih prednastavitev do zaves z "
"različnimi metodami in možnosti uporabe lastnih slik v sivinah v formatu :"
"file:`.pgm` (Portable Grey Map). Večina zaves (in enako velja za Preliv in "
"Lumo) so v bistvu pod pokrovom slike v sivih odtenkih. Med prehodom bo steza "
"sestave\\ [1]_ najprej prikazana v najtemnejšem delu slike zavese; Če je "
"prehod zavese preobrnjen, bo steza najprej vidna na najsvetlejšem območju "
"slike za zaveso."

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:28
msgid ""
"Refer to :doc:`this list <transitions/transitions_list>` of all available "
"transitions."
msgstr ""
"Glejte :doc:`ta seznam <prehodi/transitions_list>` vseh razpoložljivih "
"prehodov."

#: ../../compositing/transitions.rst:46
msgid ""
"The composition track is the one the selected clip is composited with. For "
"example, a clip on V2 overlaps with a clip on V1, and a transition is "
"created to dissolve from V2 to V1: V1 is the Composition Track."
msgstr ""
"Steza sestav je tista, s katero je sestavljen izbrani posnetek. Primer: "
"posnetek na V2 se prekriva s posnetkom na V1 in ustvarjen je prehod, ki "
"prelije iz V2 v V1: V1 je steza sestave."
